description:
Some class uses __metaclass__ for abc.ABCMeta.
six be used in general for python 3 compatibility.

For example

import abc
import six


six.add_metaclass(abc.ABCMeta)
class FooDriver:

    @abc.abstractmethod
    def bar():
        pass

